<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l13">Reıchs <expan>Ercʒtruchſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>hercʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l14"><expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
</div>
