<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l17"><expan>fürweſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ambts daʒ der <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleẅchtıgıſt fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Sıgmu<ex>n</ex>d</expan> </ab>
