<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l19"><expan>hochwırdıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>Ercʒbıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> ʒu Meıncʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l20"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> getan hab etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> den </ab>
