<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l23">der <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Meincʒ . von der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> befelhnuſſ des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l24"><expan>ſtathalt<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>fürweſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ambts daʒ <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>beſchehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey / auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex></expan> - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l25">ſchrıben . Vnd / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf yecʒ ſand Gallen tag gen vvorms ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l26"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> begert hat / als ſein gnade <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Stette<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒvm Reıche gehörıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l27">in deẅtſchen <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>deſgleıche<ex>n</ex></expan> auch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd begert hab / Da </ab>
