<ab facs="#facs_514_r1l30">brıefe . dıe <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vber das <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>ſtathalt<ex>er</ex></expan> ambt <expan>gegebe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_515" id="256v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l1">vnd auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> brıef dıe der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der künıg Vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l2">vnd den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒum Reıch gehörıg ſchreıbe . Denn wo wır eẅerr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l3"><expan>durchlewch<ex>tikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_515_r1l4"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
